      "content": "That's a good way to frame it. I also want to make sure we're being realistic about the risks. We've seen in the testing that the new model sometimes struggles with the multi-step logic required for high-end bespoke itineraries—it tends to give generic suggestions rather than the truly unique, tailored plans you provide. Should we include a disclaimer or a way for clients to reach a human if the new system fails to meet those high standards of customization?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
